---
title: Bento Style Honey Sriracha Chicken Gyozas and Prawns with Pickled Cucumber, Green Beans and Crispy Onions
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Bento Style Honey Sriracha Chicken Gyozas and Prawns in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
